map

Map<E,E[]> map()
Returns a new Map instance which will contain the first Column as key and all elements of each Row as array as map value.

The Map instance is not backed by the Table in any form, so any modifications to it will keep the Table unaffected and vice versa.

Returns:
new Map instance
See Also:
map(int), map(Map), sortedMap()
